Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE INHERITED HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ban Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this thing buried under\Nthe Field of Death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a giant floating palace...\Nor more like a gigantic bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sitting on the edge of\Nan unbelievably gigantic bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This couldn't have been done by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something this big is in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the depth\Nof Dark King Ban's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of some material\Nbetween rock and metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be floating due to some reaction\Nwith the Dark King's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Ban Palace is made of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?\NShould we escape with a Rura spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We can't run\Nand leave Dai and his father behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That explosion must have happened\Nduring their fight against Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else would explain\Nthat destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt Ban would intentionally\Nunveil Ban Palace so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find Dai and Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Ban Palace, it must have\Nan entrance from which they entered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But with it being this big...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we probably shouldn't just wander around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you saw this whole place\Nfrom above, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there anything like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the head of the bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a staircase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the entrance to\NBan Palace, the Dark Citadel Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, can you take us all there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A Rura spell will still work\Nif I can see the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, come closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Citadel Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You can see\Nwhere Dai and Baran shattered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The survivors have moved to\Nthe entrance of Ban Palace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They've gone to rescue Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do, King Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple welcome\Nwould hardly be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're honored guests to my Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Dai.\NYou wound is pretty deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... You're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have managed\Nto contain the blast, Baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that happen to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, take a good look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm certain of one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran shielded you from\Nthat massive explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,using all of his Dragonic Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, cast Behoimi on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoimi-type spells only work on\Ncreatures with life energy left in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!\NThat... That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cast Behoimi on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you... Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... see anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they all... safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! They're all alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you mustn't badger them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... beyond help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the moment of detonation...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used Doru Aura and unleashed\Nall of my Dragonic Aura...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to suppress the scale of\Nthe Black Core's blast.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My body doesn't have\Na shred of life energy left within.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No healing can save me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A real Dragon Knight... the true\NDragon Knight is unstoppable, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you won't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't weep, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the true Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the power and the magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but I lacked the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that which I lacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster that raised you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,had a far purer heart than I ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to weep over my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For you... he is your true father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa is Grampa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my real father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely hear anything anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Call out to your father\Nwith all of your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't weep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GIGABRAKE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't weep, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Though my body may perish,\Nmy soul lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be with you in the battle ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall always be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,never to part again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight on, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And defeat Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dai? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad's heart entered mine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally know...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all the things he never said...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}everything he felt...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard it all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, let's go back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I know nothing we can say\Nwill ease your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're in enemy territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know as much as we do\Nthat we can't stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean we should go charging\Nafter the Dark King right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!\NDon't you have a shred of humanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He just lost his father in front of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What can he do in this state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only option is a temporary retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain of losing a parent\Nis like a physical wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That much I know for myself.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But consider why Baran died,\Nnot just the fact that he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran died to open the way for Dai and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Hadorra\Nand his Royal Guard are gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,getting to the Dark King's palace\Nshould be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, given time,\Nthey'll regroup their forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the very chance\Nthat Baran gave us, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we retreat now,\Nhis death will have been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting for everyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Dai's father would...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... Are you really sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That means leaving your father here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad is... right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop crying and fight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to move forward.\NOtherwise, he'll yell at me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, I'll follow you to\Nthe very, very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's finish this and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go kick that Dark King's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rather bold statement,\Nyoung Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try repeating that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban, the Dark King\Nshall grant an audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. I am Dark King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!\NA decrepit old geezer just showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be easier to beat than we thought!\NMaybe we can go home early!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a letdown, right guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh come on! Somebody say something!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now things are even more\Nuncomfortable than before!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like everyone\Nalready realizes, Popp,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that King Ban is\Nfar more than meets the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's quite a shock to\Nthe former members of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You only interacted with him indirectly,\Nbut the overwhelming pressure you felt
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is still coming from the venerable\Ngentleman you see before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His calm demeanor is\Nall the more terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes you say that,\Nyou third-rate Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the same expression\NHadorra did when he first met King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to scare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I went to\Nthe trouble of coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. You made him mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on coming this far.\NI'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was certain you would be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,With Hadorra and his Royal Guard,\Nour victory seemed certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There was also the Black Core\NI implanted in Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ban Palace was supposed to\Ntake to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,only when all enemies had been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with Baran helping you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you all stand here\Nis nothing short of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd give you a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To commend your miraculous efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want most?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have to be\Nnothing other than my life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Mystban and Kilban\Nare as strong as Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if not even stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the three of us,\Nyou would have no chance of killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So I shall give you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,These two will not intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall fight you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To act without these two
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is something that\NI haven't done in centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! He's playing with us!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He truly believes that\Nwe have no chance of beating him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn him!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you won't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have fought even if you had\NMystban and the Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've all come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:53.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:05.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At last, Dark King Ban\Nappears before Dai and his friends.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even alone, Ban fights\Nwith a smile on his face.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His confidence comes from his overwhelming\NDark Aura and Magic Power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the party is driven back,\NBan unleashes his powerful magic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What will happen to Dai and his friends?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The God of The Underworld"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:04.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,
